{
  "stem": "3341.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But because I was studying up to '38 and the beginning of '39 in Brno and I didn't come home very often and I changed-- you know, you become from a teenager almost a man, I was already 19 then-- then I thought not many people will recognize me.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Especially not in this district, where I never went before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And no-- thanks God, nobody recognized me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was, for me, a big tension, you know, to, to be in a town of four hour.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes more, because they went to shopping, and there was a, a market.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, all the, all the peasants, they bring the, their produce there, to sell to get a little bit of money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they mingled and they, they have this as a gossip, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was always sitting somewhere in the corner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I didn't want to be seen, and that was very hard to tell them why.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Janko, come here, maybe you are cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or you want to go to the pub, to have a beer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I always had to find a logical answer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it was very nice of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it's also very, very dangerous for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was living in that village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly, you know, you have no idea or no view, how does it look when a front comes and changes the places?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we were occupied by Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And about a couple of weeks before I was liberated-- two weeks or maybe more-- they came suddenly early in the morning, one day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A big high-ho, they came about three lorries, German and also drawn carriages from the neighboring village.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had drums, a few, we didn't know what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was early in the morning, it was a big high-ho.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
